{"id":655556,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/【立此存照】盲人博主分享外出不便遭遇-被批优/","date":"2020-09-16T10:12:22Z","modified":"2020-09-16T10:13:20Z","title":"【立此存照】盲人博主分享外出不便遭遇 被批“优胜劣汰”","content":"<p>近日，一名盲人视频博主 @盲探-小龙蛋 发视频吐槽电梯、盲道等设施缺乏人性化设计令外出不便，未料部分“社达”（社会达尔文主义）网友回复：“这是优胜劣汰”、“为什么要城市为你服务”&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<blockquote><p>@指尖地球_：一位盲人博主的遭遇。 ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"一位盲人博主吐槽设施“不便民”  有网友回复：优胜劣汰\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3I7jL_6hTHQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">以下为部分“社达”网友回复的截图：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655567\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3pwkhgj30u00g0ac5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3pwkhgj30u00g0ac5.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3pwkhgj30u00g0ac5-300x160.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655573\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3svrnoj30u00lrq8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3svrnoj30u00lrq8e.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3svrnoj30u00lrq8e-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655566\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3p6aqoj30n00e743e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3p6aqoj30n00e743e.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3p6aqoj30n00e743e-300x185.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655568\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3qfw8sj30n007kq4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"148\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3qfw8sj30n007kq4v.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3qfw8sj30n007kq4v-300x99.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655569\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3r3emoj30n00afdj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"204\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3r3emoj30n00afdj5.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3r3emoj30n00afdj5-300x136.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655570\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rj3spj30n00600u4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"117\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rj3spj30n00600u4.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rj3spj30n00600u4-300x78.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655571\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rz0ncj30n0060abp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"117\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rz0ncj30n0060abp.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3rz0ncj30n0060abp-300x78.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655572\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3sdkv6j30n00bfjuj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"224\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3sdkv6j30n00bfjuj.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3sdkv6j30n00bfjuj-300x149.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>在网络暴力的影响之下，博主 @盲探-小龙蛋 也不得不发视频“自证盲人”：</p>\n\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-655556 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%9b%b2%e4%ba%ba%e5%8d%9a%e4%b8%bb%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%8d%e4%be%bf%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87-%e8%a2%ab%e6%89%b9%e4%bc%98/007ttgjmgy1girwet714vj30n00ze7mn/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girwet714vj30n00ze7mn-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girwet714vj30n00ze7mn-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girwet714vj30n00ze7mn-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girwet714vj30n00ze7mn-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%9b%b2%e4%ba%ba%e5%8d%9a%e4%b8%bb%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%8d%e4%be%bf%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87-%e8%a2%ab%e6%89%b9%e4%bc%98/007ttgjmgy1girw3tgslaj30n00wnarv/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3tgslaj30n00wnarv-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3tgslaj30n00wnarv-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3tgslaj30n00wnarv-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3tgslaj30n00wnarv-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%9b%b2%e4%ba%ba%e5%8d%9a%e4%b8%bb%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%8d%e4%be%bf%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87-%e8%a2%ab%e6%89%b9%e4%bc%98/007ttgjmgy1girw3u267xj30n00xdnfz/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3u267xj30n00xdnfz-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3u267xj30n00xdnfz-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3u267xj30n00xdnfz-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3u267xj30n00xdnfz-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%9b%b2%e4%ba%ba%e5%8d%9a%e4%b8%bb%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%8d%e4%be%bf%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87-%e8%a2%ab%e6%89%b9%e4%bc%98/007ttgjmgy1girw3uppm8j30n00yxdzx/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3uppm8j30n00yxdzx-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3uppm8j30n00yxdzx-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3uppm8j30n00yxdzx-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/007TTGjMgy1girw3uppm8j30n00yxdzx-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>当然，也有部分网友怒斥这些言论，同时表达了对博主的同情与声援：</p>\n<blockquote><p>@黑斗篷的猫：城市不够好，可以逐渐完善。缺乏人性，只能让社会走向错误的方向。</p>\n<p>@囗又犭苗：真牛逼，集体主义就是贡献的时候你必须为集体服务，享受权利的时候你只是个个体你没资格要求集体考虑到你？</p>\n<p>@王波粒：人均法西斯。</p>\n<p>@可爱的我不想被发现啊：昨天还和朋友吐槽这个盲道，连我们看得见的都不好走，何况看不见的人呢。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-655574\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/9b390cedgy1gisb6bjkplj20u01hcnnv.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/9b390cedgy1gisb6bjkplj20u01hcnnv.jpg 180w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/9b390cedgy1gisb6bjkplj20u01hcnnv-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/09/9b390cedgy1gisb6bjkplj20u01hcnnv-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p>@元気歪恩_：一个城市、社会、国家的文明体现是尽可能的照顾到它所有的人民。如果你觉得他不该，那么早晚你会是被抛下的那个人。</p>\n<p>@阿尔及利亚公主张秋雪：我们离“文明”的距离。</p>\n<p>@AmnesiaOfSummer：城市不就是为我服务的吗？</p>\n<p>@散装甜心：太讨厌社会达尔文主义了，一个人强大的体现并非在于对弱势者的凌驾，而在于对弱势者的帮助和爱护，社会同理。</p>\n<p>@指尖地球_：数据显示，截止至2016年，我国视力残障人士已达到1700万人，位居世界前列。但盲人基本不出门，或极少出门。除了需要陪伴，或昂贵的导盲犬外，城市建设的“不完善”是主要原因。</p>\n<p>@carry4891：“优胜劣汰”，韭菜们怎么总觉得自己能“优胜”而非“劣汰”？</p>\n<p>@felinewarrior_：中國的殘障人口比本科學歷人口要多。但是前者你在身邊看不見，因為他們在外幾乎是寸步難行。</p>\n<p>@MarcusOnTheTwee：丛林社会罢了，跟文明不沾边的。</p>\n<p>@1D6pek7gB6LfxhO：看地好难受啊坚持脸，这些人真是没有心</p>\n<p>@caocao64877141：文明洼地。</p>\n<p>@308902795：对弱势群体的态度决定一个国家的高度。</p></blockquote>\n<p>相关阅读：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"xWOC6jePGh\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/%e5%8d%97%e9%a3%8e%e7%aa%97-%e4%b8%8d%e4%bc%9a%e7%94%a8%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%89%8b%e6%9c%ba%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%8c%e8%bf%98%e6%9c%895%e4%b8%aa%e4%ba%bf/\">南风窗 | 不会用智能手机的人，还有5个亿</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"《南风窗 | 不会用智能手机的人，还有5个亿》—中国数字时代\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/%e5%8d%97%e9%a3%8e%e7%aa%97-%e4%b8%8d%e4%bc%9a%e7%94%a8%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%89%8b%e6%9c%ba%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%8c%e8%bf%98%e6%9c%895%e4%b8%aa%e4%ba%bf/embed/#?secret=xWOC6jePGh\" data-secret=\"xWOC6jePGh\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,39486],"tags":[41919,41920,41921,41923,13378,40815,33338,41922]}